{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story of the 100-day adventure of Solaris, a a Less magic power witch, and her homunculus sidekick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players choose from six daily activities to improve their abilities, learn skills, and earn money while confronting enemies. They can also develop weapons and equipment and rest to recover their strength.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The greatest feature of the game is its beautiful fully animated combat and tense battles with QTE (Quick Time Event). The variety of buffs and debuffs make the battles a pleasure to play. If you lose, you have to start over from day 1, but you will enjoy finding strategies through repeated challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The attractive characters are also not to be missed. The story is further deepened by interactions with a variety of characters who contribute to Solaris' growth, including the excellent rival wizard Tetia, the store owner August, the strict but kind mother Croise, and the three wise men Balthazar and Melchior, who manage the town.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734671492","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/page.bg.jpg?t=1734671492","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/dec772a79b58cc64ecc3e37cefd75c0d66f58d0e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734671492","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002740/dec772a79b58cc64ecc3e37cefd75c0d66f58d0e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734671492","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3400280,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story of the 100-day adventure of Solaris, a a Less magic power witch, and her homunculus sidekick.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Player